{
  "stem": "3150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then when I got out, because I was supposed to be back the day before, but they really didn't know when to look for me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But by the time I got out and I called them, it was-- it was an extra experience which I could have lived without.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was really the end of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was really getting too close for us to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my cousin-- let's see, he went, he went to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll be honest with you, maybe I shouldn't say, but I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, I just have enough of war, and I really don't want to go to Israel right now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, you're, you're crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All these years, we're all together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, Aaron, I really got to hang out longer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He left before-- he left in '47, and he went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he got to Israel-- different story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He got to Israel before Israel was a state.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Illegally, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came illegally, and he's a year older than I am, and he served in every war, '48, '56, '73, and, and '67.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And want you know, he never got a scratch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Could not believe that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was here two years ago, and never got a scratch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He has-- and now he has, he has three kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He lives in a kibbutz, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's-- he's a very happy guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got off the kibbutz once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't like it, and he went back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But none of his kids are in kibbutz anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're all off the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I've been to Israel probably six, seven times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The last time I was there was when his youngest son got married.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
